        <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;This is a quick guide to set up git with SSH ed25519 keys
not only for authenticating with GitHub or GitLab but also
for signing commits without the need to install GPG&#x2F;PGP
which has some serious &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.latacora.com&#x2F;blog&#x2F;2019&#x2F;07&#x2F;16&#x2F;the-pgp-problem&#x2F;&quot;&gt;criticisms &#x2F; flaws&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; that has led me to move
